<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>11102</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>16163</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“有钱就好了。”八戒嘟囔道，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>16164</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>19411</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这些食物看起来都很好吃。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>19412</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>23573</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>师徒四人走在朱紫国的都城里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>23574</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>29903</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>街道两边有很多人在卖食物和其他的东西。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>29904</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>34803</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“别想吃的了，八戒。”悟净说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>34804</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>37440</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那边好像出了什么事儿？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>37441</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>40867</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>唐僧指着不远处的人群问道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>40868</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>44971</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>人们在读贴在墙上的告示。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>44972</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>49233</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>师徒四人朝人群走去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>49234</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>55903</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>告示上这样写着：“朱紫国国王在寻求帮助。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>55904</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>61985</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>只要能打败妖怪，不管是谁，请到王宫来。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>61986</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>67417</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>唐僧叹了口气。“我不想耽误我们的行程。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>67418</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>70107</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但是，你们三个能打败妖怪。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>70108</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>72283</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我们得到王宫去。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>72284</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>75800</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“您别担心，师父。”悟空说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>75801</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>80069</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我很擅长打妖怪，不会花很长时间的。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>80070</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>84229</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“王宫里有食物就好了。”八戒说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>84230</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>86738</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我要饿死了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>86739</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>92068</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>师徒四人来到了王宫大门口。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>92069</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>95245</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们和一个卫兵说了情况。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>95246</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>98908</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>卫兵带他们进到宫里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>98909</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>104585</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>国王坐在王座上，看上去非常伤心。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>104586</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>109036</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“陛下。”卫兵说，“唐僧来拜见您，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>109037</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>112308</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他说他的徒弟能打败妖怪。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>112309</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>117416</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>国王抬头看了看，但什么话也没说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>117417</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>122842</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>卫兵对师徒四人小声说：“陛下非常伤心。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>122843</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>126485</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>如果能帮助陛下，请一定帮帮他。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>126486</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>134368</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空走近国王。“您好，陛下，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>134369</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>139086</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我是花果山美猴王，孙悟空。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>139087</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>145988</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>您需要有人打败妖怪。现在，我来了！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>145989</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>152207</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>国王突然双手捂着脸大哭起来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>152208</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>156741</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哦，这太可怕了！”国王哭着说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>156742</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>159412</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我再也没有希望了！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>159413</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>163337</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空挠了挠头。“您怎么了？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>163338</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>168301</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“王后——我的妻子！”国王哭喊道，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>168302</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>176120</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我可能永远......哦！太可怕了！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>176121</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>181828</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空皱了皱眉头。“陛下，您别哭了！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>181829</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>187186</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“悟空！”唐僧低声说，“你有点礼貌！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>187187</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>191194</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空没理会唐僧，看了看国王。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>191195</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>193138</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我知道您伤心。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>193139</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>196640</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>可是，如果您希望我帮您，就得冷静下来，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>196641</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>199202</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>把所有一切都告诉我。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>199203</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>203815</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>国王抽了一下鼻子，坐直了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>203816</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>209717</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你说得对。”他拿出手绢儿擤了擤鼻子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>209718</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>214106</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我告诉你发生了什么事情。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>214107</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>220931</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>三年前，一个叫赛太岁的妖怪进攻了我的王国。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>220932</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>223319</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他抓走了王后。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>223320</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>229691</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我为了救回我的妻子，派军队去打妖怪。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>229692</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>234351</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>可是，那个妖怪太厉害了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>234352</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>238103</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那个妖怪在哪儿呢？”悟空问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>238104</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>244101</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>国王起身朝窗边走去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>244102</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>251803</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他指着远处的山。“那个妖怪住在那座山里。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>53</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>251804</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>256517</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空拍了一下国王的后背。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>54</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>256518</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>261570</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“您现在不必伤心了，陛下。我会救出王后。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>55</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>261571</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>266600</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我去救王后的时候，请您照顾好我师父和师弟们。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>56</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>266601</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>271450</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>还有，八戒好像肚子饿了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>57</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>271451</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>276336</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空落到妖怪的山上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>58</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>276337</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>281298</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>几个小妖站在洞口。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>59</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>281299</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>288786</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“放了王后！不然，我就打你们！”悟空喊道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>60</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>288787</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>295788</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“啊！”小妖们边喊边跑进洞里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>61</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>295789</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>299935</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空听见洞里传来另一个声音。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>62</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>299936</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>302805</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“怎么了？”那个声音说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>63</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>302806</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>305690</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“大王！”一个小妖大喊，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>64</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>305691</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>309116</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“外面有只猴子，要我们放了王后。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>65</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>309117</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>313284</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>不然，那只猴子就要打我们！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>66</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>313285</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>318708</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一个宽肩膀的妖怪从洞里出来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>67</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>318709</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>321936</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他戴着三个铃铛。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>68</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>321937</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>328187</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我是赛太岁！”妖怪喊道，“马上离开我的山！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>69</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>328188</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>334303</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空很愤怒。“你知道我是谁吗？我是那......”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>70</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>334304</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>342053</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>嗖！火焰滚滚，烟气充满天空，沙子刮过悟空。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>71</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>342054</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>348720</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>沙子飞进鼻子，悟空咳嗽起来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>72</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>348721</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>352420</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这个太可怕了！”他大喊。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>73</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>352421</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>360452</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他捂着脸从山上跑了下来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>